	(2, 'Bridgerton: The Duke and I (Bridgertons Book 1)', 'Julia Quinn', 'Witty and entertaining, the first instalment in Julia Quinn\'s Bridgerton series serves up a sparkling romance set in the world of Regency London\'s powerful and beguiling elite.', '2020-12-01'),
	(3, 'Bridgerton: To Sir Phillip, With Love: Eloise\'s Story', 'Julia Quinn', 'Sir Phillip knew from his correspondence with his dead wife\'s distant cousin that Eloise Bridgerton was a spinster. Assuming her to be a homely figure, he could not quite believe that she was the beautiful woman on his doorstep - but are they really right for each other?', '2024-07-08'),
