	(8, 'Bridgerton: An Offer from a Gentleman: Benedict\'s Story', 'Julia Quinn', 'Sophie never dreamed she would be able to sneak into Lady Bridgerton\'s famous masquerade ball - or that her Prince Charming would be there for her! Alas she knows all enchantments must end when the clock strikes midnight.', '2024-07-08'),
