	(92, 'The Burial Plot', 'Elizabeth Macneal', 'From Elizabeth Macneal, the Sunday Times bestselling author of The Doll Factory, The Burial Plot is an unstoppable thriller about murder, manipulation, and a young woman trying to wrestle power from the hands of a dangerous man', '2024-06-06'),
