	(94, 'Daughter of Eden: Eve\'s Story', 'Jill Eileen Smith', 'The first time she opens her eyes, Eve gazes on One whose beauty nearly blinds her, whose breath is in her lungs. Her Creator takes her hand and gives her to one like her and yet different. Together, she and Adam experience pure joy as they explore Eden. But her favorite moments are when the Creator comes to walk with them, day after day.', '2024-07-08'),
