	(917, 'Sinner', 'Sierra Simone', 'Sean Bell is not a good man, and he’s never pretended to be. He doesn’t believe in goodness, God, or any happy ending that isn’t paid for in advance. There are words for men like him: playboy. Womaniser. Skirt-chaser. Sinner. When he meets a gorgeous college girl at a fundraiser, he has no problem telling her exactly what filthy things he wants to do to her — until he realizes she’s his best friend’s little sister, Zenobia \'Zenny\' Iverson, all grown up. Worse than that…she’s also about to become a nun.', '2022-10-25'),
