	(1051, 'The Taming of Ryder Cavanaugh: Number 5 in series', 'Stephanie Laurens', 'No. 1 New York Times bestselling author Stephanie Laurens has returned to another utterly irresistible branch on her beloved Cynster family tree Now that her sister Henrietta has discarded her spinster ways and become betrothed, it\'s finally Mary\'s chance for true love. She knows exactly who she wants - and it\'s not someone as wild, unmanageable and sinfully seductive as Ryder Cavanaugh. Ryder Cavanaugh, Marquess of Raventhorne, had never met a woman who wouldn\'t happily fall at his feet - or into his bed ...until Lady Mary Cynster. He soon realises he\'ll only succeed at being the man he wants to be with Mary by his side. And convincing her of that fact is just the kind of challenge that thrills him.', '2024-07-08'),
	(1052, 'The Light Between Us', 'Elaine Chiew', 'The Light Between Us is a Southeast Asian historical romance that defies time and space as an archivist explores her city\'s tumultuous past through a supernatural connection.', '2024-05-16'),
	(1053, 'An Appetite for Violets', 'Martine Bailey', 'That\'s how it is for us servants. No one pays you much heed; mostly you\'re invisible as furniture. Yet you overhear a conversation here, and add a little gossip there. A writing desk lies open and you cannot help but read a paper. Then you find something, something you should not have found.', '2024-07-08'),
