	(1607, 'A Girl\'s Own War', 'K. J. Kelly (author), Stephen Games (editor)', 'In wartime Ireland, an Englishman and a German each need the other to betray his country. And if the nationalist firebrands get their way, they may have to fight to the death. But hang on!-Just a few months ago, Flight Lieutenant Oliver Carmichael and Baron Julius von Stulpnagel were living together in Berlin, trying to sell forged paintings. So wh', '2024-07-08'),
