	(1649, 'Count Your Lucky Stars', 'Alexandria Bellefleur', 'Bellefleur has a droll, distinct voice, and her one-liners zing off the page, striking both the heart and funny bone... There\'s a sparkling quality here, one that mirrors the starry title. Bellefleur writes as if she\'s captured fairy lights in a mason jar, twinkly and lovely within something solid yet fragile.', '2022-05-04'),
