	(1769, 'Heart Of The Country', 'Tricia Stringer', 'Heart of the Country is the first book in an epic historical saga of three Australian families. Spanning several generations, this epic tells the story of the Baker, Smith and Wiltshire families forging their paths in a land both beautiful and unforgiving.', '2016-09-19'),
