	(1802, 'Dust On The Horizon', 'Tricia Stringer', 'From bestselling author Tricia Stringer, comes this compelling stand-alone historical saga, which can also be read as a sequel to Heart of the Country, the first book in the Flinders Ranges series.', '2017-01-23'),
